sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Admin Web (app.js)
    participant API as Admin Handler (Go)
    participant Store as ProviderStore
    participant DB as SQLite (call_logs / providers)

    Note over UI,DB: ① 上游管理列表加载（P0-3）
    UI->>API: GET /admin/api/providers
    API->>Store: ListProviders()
    Store->>DB: SELECT ... FROM providers (含 monthly_*_limit)
    DB-->>Store: rows
    Store-->>API: []ProviderRecord
    API-->>UI: { data: [ ProviderWithMaskedKey... ] }
    UI->>API: GET /admin/api/provider-usage
    API->>DB: SELECT provider_id, SUM(prompt_tokens+completion_tokens), SUM(effective_calls) FROM call_logs WHERE created_at >= ? GROUP BY provider_id
    DB-->>API: 各 provider 已用
    API->>Store: ListProviders() (拿 name + 限额)
    Store-->>API: providers
    API->>API: BuildProviderUsageView() + IsLowBalance() 逐 provider 合成
    API-->>UI: { data: [ ProviderUsageView... ] } (含 token_low / call_low)
    UI->>UI: 按 slug 合并，渲染两列（已用/剩余 + 进度条 + 标红）

    Note over UI,DB: ② 开账号表单切换 fixed_provider（P0-4，仅提示不拦截）
    UI->>UI: 用户选择 fixed_provider = slug
    UI->>API: GET /admin/api/providers/{slug}/usage
    API->>Store: GetProvider(slug)
    Store-->>API: ProviderRecord
    API->>DB: SELECT SUM(...) FROM call_logs WHERE provider_id = ? AND created_at >= ?
    DB-->>API: token_used, call_used
    API->>API: BuildProviderUsageView()
    API-->>UI: { data: ProviderUsageView }
    UI->>UI: 渲染「上游剩余额度」块（已用/剩余/进度条/标红）<br/>失败也【不】拦截表单提交

    Note over UI,DB: ③ 独立额度仪表盘页加载（P1-1）
    UI->>API: GET /admin/provider-usage (页面)
    API-->>UI: index.html + window.__INIT_TAB__='provider-usage'
    UI->>UI: switchTab('provider-usage')
    UI->>API: GET /admin/api/provider-usage
    API-->>UI: { data: [ ProviderUsageView... ] }
    UI->>UI: 渲染每 provider 卡片（进度条 + 低余额标红 + 窗口起点 + 更新时间）
